ğŸ–¼ï¸ IMAGE STRATEGY - 100% UNSPLASH
Oke, saya pakai 100% UNSPLASH untuk semua foto!

Kenapa Unsplash Bagus:
âœ… Free & high quality
âœ… Tidak perlu API key
âœ… Bisa langsung embed URL
âœ… Auto optimization (tinggal set width & height di URL)
âœ… Support lazy loading

Format URL Unsplash:
php
// Base URL
https://images.unsplash.com/photo-{PHOTO_ID}

// With optimization
?w=800          // width
&h=600          // height
&fit=crop       // crop to fit
&q=80           // quality 80%
&auto=format    // auto webp/jpg based on browser

// Example
https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1441986300917-64674bd600d8?w=800&h=600&fit=crop&q=80&auto=format
Untuk 50 Demo Portfolio:
