```
Nama: Website Toko Spare Part Bengkel
Features: 
  - Base E-Commerce features (keranjang, checkout, payment)
  - Industry-specific (katalog part by merk/model, VIN lookup)
  - Search by nomor part
Price: Base Ã— 1.5 multiplier (karena butuh database kompleks)
Keywords: spare part, bengkel, otomotif, jual beli part, etc
```

